findings.title: State variable that could be declared immutable
findings.description: State variables that got initialized in the constructor and then never change their values should be declared immutable to save gas.
findings.location: MissPH.sol contract, state variables initialized in the constructor

findings.title: Public function that could be declared external
findings.description: Public functions that are never called by the contract should be declared external to save gas.
findings.location: MissPH.sol contract, public functions never called from the contract
